test_large_range:
assert [3, 4, 5, 6] == [4, 5, 6]
  At index 0 diff: 3 != 4
  Left contains one more item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [4, 5, 6]
  + [3, 4, 5, 6]
  ?  +++
test_even_range:
assert [6, 8, 10, 12] == [8, 10, 12]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 8
  Left contains one more item: 12
  Full diff:
  - [8, 10, 12]
  + [6, 8, 10, 12]
  ?  +++
